<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>嵌入式 on 标仔Blog</title><link>https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/tags/%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%BC%8F/</link><description>Recent content in 嵌入式 on 标仔Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/tags/%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E5%BC%8F/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>FreeRTOS 任务调度：优先级与状态机解析</title><link>https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/posts/freertos-task-scheduling/</link><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/posts/freertos-task-scheduling/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;FreeRTOS 是最流行的开源实时操作系统，广泛应用于 MCU 项目中。本文深入解析其任务调度机制。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;任务状态机
