&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;合理设置任务优先级是 RTOS 开发的关键！&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>SPI 协议深度剖析</title><link>https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/posts/spi%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</link><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://BiaoZai1214.github.io/Bzone-blog/posts/spi%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;SPI 是嵌入式最常用的高速通信协议之一。&lt;/p&gt;

